text: Livia Reit (born 8 April 1960) is a Romanian cross-country skier. She competed in two events at the 1984 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian female cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Romania Category:Cross-country skiers at the 1984 Winter Olympics Category:People from Bran
